{"tid":2436894,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"緬甸軍方掘開女死者墳墓 稱要證明非軍方所殺","createTime":"2021-03-07T13:11:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T13:38:02.000Z","uid":362346,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"abace566c24297d0fd80be7c82f6fe30d14b76c1","tid":2436894,"uid":362346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:11:13.000Z","msg":"緬甸示威者新墳遭挖惹眾怒　軍方撿鉛片證死者非警員槍殺<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r9PgzDT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr9PgzDT.jpg&h=28be4726&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n緬甸軍成了部分國民之恨，現在更有緬甸人在黑夜中拍到，這群緬甸軍在黑夜中挖開墳墓，而且據說他們開挖的，竟然就是前幾天，被軍方開槍爆頭的19歲少女鄧家希。 示威者：「這裡有手套他們用了刀子，手套上還有血跡。」<br />\n<br />\n從畫面中可以看到，緬甸軍人挖起棺木後，隨隨便便重新埋起土裏，民眾發現現場血跡斑斑，都是軍方留下的染血的手術器具，引起民眾撻伐炮轟軍方挖屍，是對少女和家人的侮辱。<br />\n<br />\n（編按：軍方將她的棺木挖出來，並將遺體置於長椅上，並從她身上取出一小片鉛，稱從這件面積為1.2厘米乘0.7厘米異物，與警察所用子彈不同，並指令她中彈的武器，是能發射點三八子彈的。緬甸國營電視台引述軍方稱，「所以，這是那些不想政局穩定的人進行暗殺」。<br />\n<br />\n根據路透社所拍現場照片，鄧家希死前一刻，是背向軍警而坐，曾看向軍警，但在她轉頭看向相反方向後中彈。<br />\n<br />\n電視台亦報道，軍方進行驗屍前曾徵詢死者家屬同意，但沒說他們是否已同意。路透社稱無法與死者家屬聯絡得上。）<br />\n[url]http://（編按：軍方將她的棺木挖出來，並將遺體置於長椅上，並從她身上取出一小片鉛，稱從這件面積為1.2厘米乘0.7厘米異物，與警察所用子彈不同，並指令她中彈的武器，是能發射點三八子彈的。緬甸國營電視台引述軍方稱，「所以，這是那些不想政局穩定的人進行暗殺」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AS5SSrp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAS5SSrp.png&h=0d254c47&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wehuac5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWehuac5.png&h=4ef4dfa7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u0RCi6r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu0RCi6r.png&h=40d037b3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qxJExrs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqxJExrs.png&h=dbeb136c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UZzsGjO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUZzsGjO.png&h=5475d2a4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2aDExru.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2aDExru.png&h=faffb7ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n緬甸人的憤怒還發洩在與軍政府有關的企業，緬甸啤酒就因為軍系色彩太濃，不但營收直直落，原本的合作企業，日本的麒麟啤酒，現在也宣布與他們終止合約。 記者旁白：「從2月1日以來至少有55人喪命，而且是和平示威下遇害，其中超過半數死者都是年輕人，25歲以下年輕人17人是20歲以下。」 眼見局勢持續惡化，緬甸人只能期待來自國際的援助和介入，能早日到來。"},{"pid":"774937d82affe9d9b7357cbfeb2bf2b45a6da36a","tid":2436894,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:12:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e23a2a2fd1df01910087127cf263c51bc13cc99","tid":2436894,"uid":138868,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:13:32.000Z","msg":"點224痰罐仔子彈<br />\n我專用嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dec85e8f0deefe1b74cb68b97c8596440bb569cb","tid":2436894,"uid":362346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"774937d82affe9d9b7357cbfeb2bf2b45a6da36a","tid":2436894,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:12:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:17:03.000Z","msg":"手足.."},{"pid":"d111b49b40f51524f2305d96a2c612beac6f3adc","tid":2436894,"uid":362346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e23a2a2fd1df01910087127cf263c51bc13cc99","tid":2436894,"uid":138868,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:13:32.000Z","msg":"點224痰罐仔子彈<br />\n我專用嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:17:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/linguistic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/linguistic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/linguistic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aefc8eecd836c8fa7